@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted">
        Your privacy is very important to <span class="textLightPurple fw-bold">KODLA</span> team. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our online courses and services.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-4" />

    <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
        We collect various types of information to enhance your learning experience. This includes personal details such as your name, email address, and payment information when you register for a course. Additionally, we may collect usage data and preferences to personalize your learning journey.
    </p>

    <h2 class="h4 mt-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>
        Your information is used to process your course registrations, improve our services, and send you important updates about new courses or features. We may also use aggregated data to analyze trends and better understand our user base, ensuring that our content remains relevant and engaging.
    </p>

    <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
        We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. Information may be shared with trusted partners only when necessary to provide you with a seamless course experience or as required by law.
    </p>

    <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Security</h2>
    <p>
        We are committed to safeguarding your information and have implemented appropriate security measures to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse. However, no system is entirely foolproof, and we recommend that you take steps to secure your account.
    </p>

    <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
        You have the right to review, update, or delete your personal information at any time. If you have any questions or concerns about your data, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-5 text-center">
        <small class="text-muted">Effective Date: April 2025</small>
    </p>
</div>
